<db:abstract>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qstyleoptiongraphicsitem.xml">QStyleOptionGraphicsItem</db:link> class is used to describe the parameters needed to draw a <db:link xlink:href="qgraphicsitem.xml">QGraphicsItem</db:link>.</db:para>
<db:para>This class was introduced in Qt 4.2.</db:para>
